en_question:
    \noindent\textbf{4.4} A certain blended liquor product is sold under three brands: Red, Yellow, and Blue. All are made by blending three grades of base liquor: Grade I, II, and III. The daily supply and cost per kilogram of each grade of base liquor are provided in Table 4-13, and the blending requirements and selling prices for each branded product are given in Table 4-14. The decision-maker has specified the following prioritized conditions: 1.Each branded liquor must strictly follow its specified blending proportions. 2.Profit must be maximized. 3.At least 2,000 kg of Red brand liquor must be produced per day. 

\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \caption{Table 4-13: Daily Supply and Cost of Base Liquors}
    \label{tab:raw_material}
    \begin{tabular}{ccc}
        \toprule
        Grade & Daily Supply (kg) & Cost (Yuan/kg) \\
        \midrule
        I   & 1500 & 6.0 \\
        II  & 2000 & 4.5 \\
        III & 1000 & 3.0 \\
        \bottomrule
    \end{tabular}
\end{table}

\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \caption{Table 4-14: Blending Requirements and Selling Prices of Branded Liquors}
    \label{tab:product_requirements}
    \begin{tabular}{ccc}
        \toprule
        Brand & Blending Requirements (\%) & Selling Price (Yuan/kg) \\
        \midrule
        Red  & Grade III < 10\%, Grade I > 50\% & 5.5 \\
        Yellow  & Grade III < 70\%, Grade I > 20\% & 5.0 \\
        Blue  & Grade III < 50\%, Grade I > 10\% & 4.8 \\
        \bottomrule
    \end{tabular}
\end{table}

cn_question:
    \noindent\textbf{4.4} 某成品酒有三种商标（红、黄、蓝），都是由三种原料酒（等级 I、II、III）兑制而成。
三种等级的原料酒的日供应量和成本见表 4-13，三种商标的成品酒的兑制要求和销售价见表 4-14。
决策者规定：首先是必须严格按比例兑制各商标的酒，其次是获利最大；最后是红商标的酒每天至少生产 $\geq$ 2000kg。

\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \caption{原料酒日供应量和成本}
    \label{tab:raw_material}
    \begin{tabular}{ccc}
        \toprule
        等级 & 日供应量 (kg) & 成本 (元/kg) \\
        \midrule
        I   & 1500 & 6.0 \\
        II  & 2000 & 4.5 \\
        III & 1000 & 3.0 \\
        \bottomrule
    \end{tabular}
\end{table}

\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \caption{成品酒兑制要求和售价}
    \label{tab:product_requirements}
    \begin{tabular}{ccc}
        \toprule
        商标 & 兑制要求 (\%) & 售价 (元/kg) \\
        \midrule
        红  & III 少于 10\%，I 多于 50\% & 5.5 \\
        黄  & III 少于 70\%，I 多于 20\% & 5.0 \\
        蓝  & III 少于 50\%，I 多于 10\% & 4.8 \\
        \bottomrule
    \end{tabular}
\end{table}
